---
title: Roasted Mexican Corn (v) with Tomato Rice, Kidney Beans and Guac
description: The taste of warm, buttery sweet corn on the cob is hard to beat, especially when it’s marinated in our special Mexican spice rub. Served with Mexican-style beans and rice, creamy homemade guacamole and a drizzle of cooling sour cream, this deliciously simple dish is perfect for a quick-fix supper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-mexican-corn-5ce37cc7-3274d3fb.jpg
